B.MV=new A.dy("Klomi airbnb","Klomi airbnb is the clone of famous Airbnb app.\nWelcome to Klomi, your ultimate Airbnb clone experience! Discover the convenience and excitement of our platform, designed to provide you with a seamless and user-friendly accommodation booking process. With a vast selection of properties and unique stays, finding your perfect home away from home has never been easier. Whether you're looking for a cozy apartment in the heart of the city or a luxurious villa by the beach, Klomi has it all. Our secure and reliable platform ensures a hassle-free booking experience, allowing you to focus on creating unforgettable memories during your stay. Start your adventure with Klomi today!","https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/my-converter-flutter.appspot.com/o/app_logos%2Fklomi.png?alt=media&token=ec2c4d25-bb37-4dbb-8f42-fa3323e08e27","","",B.nU,B.HY,"","",B.Gt)
